Proc.src: CREATE DEFINER=`root`@`localhost` FUNCTION `fn_ConsecutivoByTipoDocumento`(`id_tipo_documento` INT) RETURNS int(11) NO SQL RETURN (SELECT tipo_documento.consecutivo_inicial FROM tipo_documento WHERE tipo_documento.id = id_tipo_documento AND tipo_documento.deleted_at IS NULL) + (SELECT Count(a.tipo_id) AS consecutivo FROM auxiliar_consecutivo AS a WHERE a.deleted_at IS NULL AND a.tipo_id = id_tipo_documento )

CREATE DEFINER=`root`@`localhost` PROCEDURE `getAllGuias`(IN `id_age` INT(11)) NO SQL SELECT guia_hija.id AS guia_hija_id, guia_hija.num_guia AS nume_guia, consignee.nombre_full AS cons_nomfull, shipper.nombre_full AS ship_nomfull, guia_hija.peso AS peso, guia_hija.volumen AS volumen, agencia.descripcion AS nom_agencia, guia_hija.created_at, guia_hija.consolidado FROM guia_hija INNER JOIN shipper ON guia_hija.shipper_id = shipper.id INNER JOIN consignee ON guia_hija.consignee_id = consignee.id INNER JOIN agencia ON guia_hija.agencia_id = agencia.id WHERE guia_hija.deleted_at IS NULL

CREATE DEFINER=`root`@`localhost` PROCEDURE `getAllWarehouseDetalle`(IN `id_agencia` INT(11)) NO SQL IF id_agencia = 0 THEN SELECT guia_hija_detalle.id, guia_hija_detalle.consolidado, guia_hija_detalle.num_consolidado, guia_hija_detalle.guia_hija_id, guia_hija_detalle.tipo_empaque_id, guia_hija_detalle.posicion_arancelaria_id, guia_hija_detalle.dimensiones, guia_hija_detalle.largo, guia_hija_detalle.ancho, guia_hija_detalle.alto, guia_hija_detalle.peso, guia_hija_detalle.contenido, guia_hija_detalle.tracking, guia_hija_detalle.volumen, guia_hija_detalle.valor, guia_hija_detalle.num_guia, guia_hija_detalle.created_at, guia_hija_detalle.num_warehouse, guia_hija_detalle.estado, guia_hija.num_guia AS nume_guia, guia_hija.shipper_id, guia_hija.consignee_id, guia_hija.consolidado, agencia.descripcion AS nom_agencia, posicion_arancelaria.pa AS nom_pa, shipper.nombre_full AS ship_nomfull, consignee.nombre_full AS cons_nomfull, guia_hija_detalle.deleted_at FROM guia_hija_detalle INNER JOIN guia_hija ON guia_hija_detalle.guia_hija_id = guia_hija.id LEFT OUTER JOIN posicion_arancelaria ON posicion_arancelaria.id = guia_hija_detalle.posicion_arancelaria_id LEFT OUTER JOIN agencia ON guia_hija.agencia_id = agencia. id LEFT OUTER JOIN consignee ON guia_hija.consignee_id = consignee.id AND consignee.agencia_id=agencia.id LEFT OUTER JOIN shipper ON guia_hija.shipper_id = shipper.id AND shipper.agencia_id=agencia.id WHERE guia_hija_detalle.deleted_at IS NULL AND guia_hija.deleted_at IS NULL ORDER BY guia_hija.created_at DESC; ELSE SELECT guia_hija_detalle.id, guia_hija_detalle.consolidado, guia_hija_detalle.num_consolidado, guia_hija_detalle.guia_hija_id, guia_hija_detalle.tipo_empaque_id, guia_hija_detalle.posicion_arancelaria_id, guia_hija_detalle.dimensiones, guia_hija_detalle.largo, guia_hija_detalle.ancho, guia_hija_detalle.alto, guia_hija_detalle.peso, guia_hija_detalle.contenido, guia_hija_detalle.tracking, guia_hija_detalle.volumen, guia_hija_detalle.valor, guia_hija_detalle.num_guia, guia_hija_detalle.created_at, guia_hija_detalle.num_warehouse, guia_hija_detalle.estado, guia_hija.num_guia AS nume_guia, guia_hija.shipper_id, guia_hija.consignee_id, guia_hija.consolidado, agencia.descripcion AS nom_agencia, posicion_arancelaria.pa AS nom_pa, shipper.nombre_full AS ship_nomfull, consignee.nombre_full AS cons_nomfull, guia_hija_detalle.deleted_at FROM guia_hija_detalle INNER JOIN guia_hija ON guia_hija_detalle.guia_hija_id = guia_hija.id LEFT OUTER JOIN posicion_arancelaria ON posicion_arancelaria.id = guia_hija_detalle.posicion_arancelaria_id LEFT OUTER JOIN agencia ON guia_hija.agencia_id = agencia. id LEFT OUTER JOIN consignee ON guia_hija.consignee_id = consignee.id AND consignee.agencia_id=agencia.id LEFT OUTER JOIN shipper ON guia_hija.shipper_id = shipper.id AND shipper.agencia_id=agencia.id WHERE guia_hija_detalle.deleted_at IS NULL AND guia_hija.deleted_at IS NULL AND guia_hija.is_wrh_guia = 1 AND guia_hija.agencia_id = id_agencia ORDER BY guia_hija.created_at DESC; END IF

CREATE DEFINER=`root`@`localhost` PROCEDURE `getConsecutivoByTipoDocumento`(IN `id_tipo_documento` INT, IN `id_documento` INT, IN `fecha` TIMESTAMP) NO SQL BEGIN SELECT fn_ConsecutivoByTipoDocumento(id_tipo_documento) AS consecutivo;
INSERT INTO auxiliar_consecutivo (documento_id,tipo_id,created_at) VALUES (id_documento, id_tipo_documento,fecha); END

CREATE DEFINER=`root`@`localhost` PROCEDURE `getDatosConsolidacionByNumGuia`(IN `num_guia` VARCHAR(20)) NO SQL SELECT a.id, a.consolidado, a.num_consolidado, a.guia_hija_id, d.id AS ship_id, d.primer_nombre AS ship_nom1, d.segundo_nombre AS ship_nom2, d.primer_apellido AS ship_ape1, d.segundo_apellido AS ship_ape2, d.nombre_full AS ship_nomfull, c.id AS cons_id, c.primer_nombre AS cons_nom1, c.segundo_nombre AS cons_nom2, c.primer_apellido AS cons_ape1, c.segundo_apellido AS cons_ape2, c.nombre_full AS cons_nomfull, a.num_guia, a.num_warehouse, a.estado, b.piezas, e.id AS id_ciudad, f.id AS id_estado, g.id AS id_pais, i.id AS id_pa, i.pa, a.declarado2, a.peso2, a.contenido2, a.p FROM guia_hija_detalle AS a INNER JOIN guia_hija AS b ON a.guia_hija_id = b.id INNER JOIN consignee AS c ON b.consignee_id = c.id INNER JOIN shipper AS d ON b.shipper_id = d.id INNER JOIN localizacion AS e ON e.id = c.localizacion_id INNER JOIN deptos AS f ON f.id = e.deptos_id INNER JOIN pais AS g ON g.id = f.pais_id INNER JOIN posicion_arancelaria AS i ON a.posicion_arancelaria_id = i.id WHERE (a.num_guia = num_guia COLLATE utf8_unicode_ci OR a.num_warehouse = num_guia COLLATE utf8_unicode_ci) AND a.deleted_at IS NULL

CREATE DEFINER=`root`@`localhost` PROCEDURE `getDatosInformeWarehouseById`(IN `id_wrh` INT) NO SQL SELECT a.id AS id, a.usuario_id, a.shipper_id, a.consignee_id, a.mal_empacado AS malEmpaque, a.rota AS rota, a.re_empacado AS reEmpaque, a.carga_peligrosa AS peligro, a.factura AS factura, a.piezas AS piezas, a.peso AS peso, a.volumen AS vol, a.observaciones AS observacion, a.created_at AS fechaCrea, a.agencia_id AS id_agencia, d.id AS id_ship, d.localizacion_id AS ship_localizacion, d.nombre_full AS ship_nomfull, d.direccion AS ship_dir, d.telefono AS ship_tel, d.correo AS ship_email, d.zip AS ship_zip, b.id AS cons_id, b.tipo_identificacion_id AS cons_tipo_id, b.localizacion_id AS cons_localiz_id, b.documento AS cons_doc, b.nombre_full AS cons_nomfull, b.direccion AS cons_dir, b.telefono AS cons_tel, b.correo AS cons_email, b.zip AS cons_zip, b.celular AS cons_cel, b.tarifa AS cons_tarifa, b.po_box AS cons_poBox, b.estado AS cons_estado, c.descripcion AS agencia_des, c.localizacion_id AS agencia_localizacion, c.direccion AS agencia_dir, c.responsable AS agencia_responsable, c.zip AS agencia_zip, c.telefono AS agencia_tel FROM guia_hija AS a INNER JOIN consignee AS b ON a.consignee_id = b.id INNER JOIN agencia AS c ON a.agencia_id = c.id INNER JOIN shipper AS d ON a.shipper_id = d.id WHERE a.id = id_wrh AND a.deleted_at IS NULL

CREATE DEFINER=`root`@`localhost` PROCEDURE `getDetalleConsolidadoById`(IN `id_conso` INT(11)) NO SQL SELECT c.estado, b.num_bolsa, c.num_guia, c.num_warehouse, d.nombre_full AS nom_cons, c.contenido2, f.pa AS arancel, f.id AS arancel_id, c.declarado2, c.peso2, Count(c.id) AS piezas, e.nombre_full AS nom_ship, a.id, b.id AS id_detalle, b.is_guia, c.id AS id_guia_detalle, d.id AS id_cons, e.id AS id_ship FROM consolidado AS a INNER JOIN consolidado_detalle AS b ON b.consolidado_id = a.id INNER JOIN guia_hija_detalle AS c ON c.id = b.guia_hija_detalle_id INNER JOIN consignee AS d ON c.consignee_id = d.id INNER JOIN shipper AS e ON c.shipper_id = e.id INNER JOIN posicion_arancelaria AS f ON c.arancel_id2 = f.id WHERE a.deleted_at IS NULL AND c.deleted_at IS NULL AND a.id = id_conso GROUP BY c.estado, b.num_bolsa, c.num_guia, d.nombre_full, e.nombre_old, c.contenido2, f.pa, f.id, c.declarado2, c.peso2

CREATE DEFINER=`root`@`localhost` PROCEDURE `getGuiasDisponiblesByFechas`(IN `id_age` INT(11), IN `fecha_ini` VARCHAR(20), IN `fecha_fin` VARCHAR(20)) NO SQL SELECT a.id, a.guia_hija_id, a.num_guia, a.peso2, a.declarado2, a.shipper_id, a.consignee_id, DATE_FORMAT(a.created_at,'%Y-%m-%d') as created_at FROM guia_hija_detalle AS a INNER JOIN guia_hija AS b ON b.id = a.guia_hija_id WHERE a.deleted_at IS NULL AND a.consolidado = 0 AND b.agencia_id = id_age AND a.created_at BETWEEN fecha_ini AND fecha_fin

CREATE DEFINER=`root`@`localhost` PROCEDURE `getIdGuiaDetalleByTracking`(IN `track` VARCHAR(100)) NO SQL SELECT guia_hija_detalle.id FROM guia_hija_detalle INNER JOIN guia_hija ON guia_hija_detalle.guia_hija_id = guia_hija.id WHERE guia_hija.is_wrh_guia = 1 AND guia_hija_detalle.tracking = track COLLATE utf8_unicode_ci AND guia_hija_detalle.deleted_at IS NULL AND guia_hija.deleted_at IS NULL

CREATE DEFINER=`root`@`localhost` PROCEDURE `getInformeConsolidadoById`(IN `id_conso` INT(11)) NO SQL SELECT a.num_guia, a.num_warehouse, d.id AS ship_id, d.nombre_full AS ship_nom, d.direccion AS ship_dir, d.telefono AS ship_tel, c.id AS cons_id, c.direccion AS cons_dir, c.telefono AS cons_tel, c.nombre_full AS cons_nom, a.declarado2 AS declarado2, a.peso2 AS peso2, a.contenido2 AS contenido2, d.localizacion_id AS ship_localidad_id, c.localizacion_id AS cons_localidad_id, b.consolidado_id, b.num_bolsa, b.created_at, b.is_guia, e.pa, g.descripcion AS agencia FROM guia_hija_detalle AS a INNER JOIN consolidado_detalle AS b ON b.guia_hija_detalle_id = a.id INNER JOIN consignee AS c ON c.id = a.consignee_id INNER JOIN shipper AS d ON d.id = a.shipper_id INNER JOIN posicion_arancelaria AS e ON a.arancel_id2 = e.id INNER JOIN guia_hija AS f ON a.guia_hija_id = f.id INNER JOIN agencia AS g ON f.agencia_id = g.id WHERE b.deleted_at IS NULL AND b.consolidado_id = id_conso

CREATE DEFINER=`root`@`localhost` PROCEDURE `getNumWarehousesByIdWhr`(IN `id_wrh` INT(11)) NO SQL SELECT guia_hija_detalle.num_warehouse FROM guia_hija_detalle WHERE guia_hija_detalle.guia_hija_id = id_wrh AND guia_hija_detalle.deleted_at IS NULL

CREATE DEFINER=`root`@`localhost` PROCEDURE `getStatusDetalleByIdGuia`(IN `id_guia` INT(11)) NO SQL SELECT guia_hija_detalle.id AS guia_id, guia_hija_detalle.num_warehouse, guia_hija_detalle.num_guia, `status`.descripcion, usuario.user_name, status_detalle.id, `status`.id AS status_id, usuario.id AS usuario_id, status_detalle.fecha_status, status_detalle.observacion FROM status_detalle INNER JOIN guia_hija_detalle ON guia_hija_detalle.id = status_detalle.guia_hija_detalle_id INNER JOIN `status` ON `status`.id = status_detalle.status_id INNER JOIN usuario ON status_detalle.usuario_id = usuario.id WHERE status_detalle.guia_hija_detalle_id = id_guia AND status_detalle.deleted_at IS NULL ORDER BY status_detalle.created_at DESC

CREATE DEFINER=`root`@`localhost` PROCEDURE `getStatusDetalleByIdGuiaDetalle`(IN `id_guia` INT(11)) NO SQL SELECT status_detalle.id, status_detalle.status_id, status_detalle.usuario_id, status_detalle.guia_hija_detalle_id, status_detalle.fecha_status, status_detalle.transportadora, status_detalle.num_transportadora, status_detalle.created_at, `status`.descripcion, status_detalle.observacion, guia_hija_detalle.shipper_id, shipper.nombre_full, guia_hija_detalle.peso, guia_hija_detalle.tracking, guia_hija_detalle.num_guia, guia_hija_detalle.num_warehouse, guia_hija.is_wrh_guia FROM status_detalle INNER JOIN `status` ON status_detalle.status_id = `status`.id INNER JOIN guia_hija_detalle ON status_detalle.guia_hija_detalle_id = guia_hija_detalle.id INNER JOIN shipper ON guia_hija_detalle.shipper_id = shipper.id INNER JOIN guia_hija ON guia_hija_detalle.guia_hija_id = guia_hija.id WHERE status_detalle.guia_hija_detalle_id = id_guia AND status_detalle.deleted_at IS NULL AND `status`.deleted_at IS NULL ORDER BY status_detalle.created_at DESC

CREATE DEFINER=`root`@`localhost` PROCEDURE `getWarehouseById`(IN `id_wrh` INT(11)) NO SQL SELECT guia_hija.id, guia_hija.consignee_id, guia_hija.shipper_id, guia_hija.agencia_id, guia_hija.piezas, guia_hija.peso, guia_hija.volumen, guia_hija.peso_cobrado, guia_hija.created_at, guia_hija.factura, guia_hija.carga_peligrosa, guia_hija.re_empacado, guia_hija.mal_empacado, guia_hija.rota, guia_hija.estado, guia_hija.num_warehouse, guia_hija.num_guia, guia_hija.usuario_id, guia_hija.observaciones FROM guia_hija WHERE guia_hija.id = id_wrh AND guia_hija.deleted_at IS NULL

CREATE DEFINER=`root`@`localhost` PROCEDURE `getWarehouseDetalleByIdWarehouse`(IN `id_wrh` INT(11), IN `is_detalle` INT(11)) NO SQL IF is_detalle = 0 THEN SELECT guia_hija_detalle.id, guia_hija_detalle.guia_hija_id, guia_hija_detalle.tipo_empaque_id, guia_hija_detalle.dimensiones, guia_hija_detalle.peso, guia_hija_detalle.largo, guia_hija_detalle.ancho, guia_hija_detalle.alto, guia_hija_detalle.contenido, guia_hija_detalle.tracking, guia_hija_detalle.volumen, guia_hija_detalle.estado, guia_hija_detalle.num_warehouse, guia_hija_detalle.created_at FROM guia_hija_detalle WHERE guia_hija_detalle.guia_hija_id = id_wrh AND guia_hija_detalle.deleted_at IS NULL; ELSE SELECT guia_hija_detalle.id, guia_hija_detalle.guia_hija_id, guia_hija_detalle.tipo_empaque_id, guia_hija_detalle.dimensiones, guia_hija_detalle.peso, guia_hija_detalle.largo, guia_hija_detalle.ancho, guia_hija_detalle.alto, guia_hija_detalle.contenido, guia_hija_detalle.tracking, guia_hija_detalle.volumen, guia_hija_detalle.estado, guia_hija_detalle.num_warehouse, guia_hija_detalle.created_at FROM guia_hija_detalle WHERE guia_hija_detalle.id = id_wrh AND guia_hija_detalle.deleted_at IS NULL; END IF
